  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Although their parents already might have said, hey, kill the Jew, or beat him them up, or shoot him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But it was highly-- you ask me before and I repeat-- camaraderie among the kids.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Didn't change much.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Laws-- it wasn't a matter of laws against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is-- when you have an industry where you produce this material but everybody has to use it, especially in '39 toward '40, you had already what you call the aspect and everything, the smell of the gunpowder, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you knew something is cooking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that's long-- you-- the production in our sawmill, everything produced for the-- for them what they needed for improvised hangar for the airplanes before the front.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And any kind of wood, you know, you need this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All these boards are very important like even today, and so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was not like you felt-- you just had to watch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You wouldn't want to, like I mentioned before, you wouldn't go out after you ate your supper, your dinner for a walk, because someone will catch up with you no matter what, would beat you up, or so.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
